    Black Aracnia got closer, and began to seductivly scratch on his abdomen, 
teaseing it. "Remember Hell Beast? The great and powerful war lord who led us 
into countless victory's over our enemy's?"
    She didnt wait for a responce. " Well, he actually left me in charge when 
he left so adbruptly. But then that big old mean Rampage decided he would 
command. What could I do? Im just a little bot. I need a big strong bot like 
you to help me."
    Then, smiling, she said, "Would you help me? Please?"
